OL,3,C'It took over my whole life':
OL,4,CCustomers on new British gas bill
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FBritish Gas said the change to a new
OL,8,Fbilling system has been seamless - but
OL,9,Fsome customers disagree, as ITV News
OL,10,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,12,FBritish Gas customers have been
OL,13,Fcontacting ITV News with concerns
OL,14,Fabout customer service. The company is
OL,15,Fcompleting the move of 7.5 million
OL,16,Faccounts to a new billing system.
OL,18,FIt says that change, which started in
OL,19,F2022, has gone seamlessly - and has
OL,20,Fimproved things, but some customers
OL,21,Fdisagree.
