OL,3,C'It took over my whole life':
OL,4,CCustomers on new British gas bill
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FDebbie Kerslake showed ITV News her
OL,8,Funbelievable bills. She somehow ended
OL,9,Fup with four accounts and said the
OL,10,Fdisputed demands coincided with a move
OL,11,Fto the new British gas billing system
OL,12,Ftwo years ago.
OL,14,FShe said: "I had a normal account, the
OL,15,Fnext minute, four accounts on two
OL,16,Fdifferent platforms - and it took over
OL,17,Fmy whole life."
