OL,4,CCustomers on new British gas bill
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThe Energy Ombudsman found "a poor
OL,8,Flevel of service", and told Debbie
OL,9,FKerslake: "In October 2022, British
OL,10,FGas started the process of moving you
OL,11,Fto their new billing platform.
OL,12,FHowever, they have had a great number
OL,13,Fof problems with this process."
OL,15,FBritish Gas told ITV News there is no
OL,16,Fproblem with its new billing system,
OL,17,Fand it sees Debbie's as an isolated
OL,18,Fsituation which they resolved.
