OL,7,FIt says it originally arose when the
OL,8,Ffirm got wrong information from an
OL,9,Findustry database.
OL,11,FITV News also met Wendy Fletcher, who
OL,12,Fsuffered with yo-yo bills. Within a
OL,13,Fmonth, her British Gas account bounced
OL,14,Ffrom credit to more than #400 in debit.
OL,16,FShe spoke to a customer advisor who
OL,17,Ftold her: "It's a fault which has
OL,18,Faffected a small amount of customers
OL,19,Fwhen the accounts have migrated across
OL,20,Fto the new system."
