OL,12,FThe company apologised for the error,
OL,13,Fwhich its said was quickly resolved
OL,14,Flast December with no financial loss.
OL,16,FBritish Gas says its new billing
OL,17,Fsystem has improved customer service,
OL,18,Freflected in independent surveys, such
OL,19,Fas Uswitch. However, some consumer
OL,20,Fgroups have concerns.
