OL,3,C'It took over my whole life':
OL,4,CCustomers on new British gas bill
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FEmily Seymour, from Which?, said: "A
OL,8,Fnumber of British Gas customers have
OL,9,Ftold us that they've experienced poor
OL,10,Fcustomer service - and when we asked
OL,11,Fthem about what has happened and why,
OL,12,Fthey told us that it was to do with
OL,13,Ftheir migration process."
OL,15,FBritish Gas says its new billing
OL,16,Fsystem has earned it praise for better
OL,17,Fcustomer service, but some ITV News
OL,18,Fhas spoken to won't be giving it any
OL,19,Fawards.
